<a name="2">[2]</a> <a href="#2" id=2>Present machines have almost no emotional qualities, and, in my opinion, it would be a bad idea to give them any.</a>
<a name="3">[3]</a> <a href="#3" id=3>It is also common to ascribe personalities to cars, boats, and other machinery.</a>
